Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.23,hinamatsuri_hm1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,542)}黑幫特别篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.23,hinamatsuri_hm1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,978)}當代黑幫現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:06.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有什麼意見或建議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,局長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想對一個男的進行跟蹤採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是蘆川組的新田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本身是個智力派的黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:22.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,卻在之前的對抗中一個人端了敵對的筱冢全組
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是個相當有傳奇色彩的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:28.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,據說他們的正當收入還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這種有著昭和氣息的黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會吸引一波觀眾的眼球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮 瀨田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:45.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於被任命為了負責人啊 一定要把它給干好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 我瀨田大介的取材開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然會是一次危險的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:58.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但也會測試出我一個記者到底有多大實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,紀錄片取材
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟蹤採訪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:05.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是新田義史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:15.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乍一看還是挺沉穩的 不知道他的內心究竟有多麼殘暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 要是就拍我一個人就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:22.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然黑幫上的人不能用一般手段搞定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在黑幫業界 最勢如破竹的就是新田先生你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以讓我為你拍攝你成為一代梟雄的序章嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拍下真實的你 就必將成為傳奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:42.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是把性命賭在了這上邊 絕對不可以退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:50.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 關於這位實打實的武鬥派
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田義史的跟蹤採訪開始了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.30,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:06.40,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の面影思い出す　ふとした時に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:27.48,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:33.21,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.01,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.82,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.63,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.99,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.76,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:56.19,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.44,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:07.25,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.74,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:06.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:27.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:33.21,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:56.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:07.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
