Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.97,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\an8\c&HFFFFFF&}第十一話 渴求血與暴力與金錢的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:35.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在腳骨折了 順便送她一程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:46.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 你是怎麼成為黑幫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大學時代本來想創辦公司就去做了兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我兼職的地方就有黑幫背景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:56.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接觸得多了 就覺得成為黑幫的話或許會賺得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是為了賺錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是為了賺錢 但錢也不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也有一些人情世故在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親很早就去世了 我想幫家裡做些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 是因為這種理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此啊 是為了你的家人或者女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我女兒 我只是收養她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是被逼無奈 被逼無奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟沒別人會養你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟女人的關係如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說黑幫在男女關係方面比較豪爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前確實是喜歡過一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她是那種把別人利用完就扔開的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那女兒你跟新田住在一起感覺如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他會給我做飯 新田是個大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這麼讓人難為情的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你被收養之前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總是被要求幹這個幹那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是個好人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田的肉丸比我多一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來來軒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 秒殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的 他肯定是對我們隱藏了本性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不肯輕易露出真面目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥的戰鬥史？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有沒有 因為我哥是個樂於助人的好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥史的話還得說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 我還去抓過小混混來打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好當做空手道的練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還能練練危險動作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後最後被學校停課了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,採訪新田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:57.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子 你還真是了不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要給我組長添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的計劃正逐步偏離正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:06.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去看老爺子的慰問品買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了 我現在馬上去買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 長點心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該發更大火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那傢伙很笨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是整天都發火的話會很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底要隱藏本性到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全搞錯了 黑幫要是這樣的話會被觀眾看不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊大哥 動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我決不允許大哥被全國人民瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:46.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來來來 用這個向全國觀眾證明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是有這個幹勁的話 倒是用到工作上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱們就從開頭開始來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟班 去看老爺子的慰問品買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,壞了 那個 我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就去買
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？你給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在耍我嗎 你這個笨蛋呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且灰都灑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一直跟你說要好好打掃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我馬上打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了一段好東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你也砸得太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你們誰給我拿個醫護包過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這之後還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這就要回去了嗎 晚上不去玩玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我得回家給雛做晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是白…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是腸胃藥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:45.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 難道說他真的就是一個好人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨田 取材怎麼樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,局長 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍到了相當勁爆的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一股黑幫仍未覆滅的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:01.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確是被逼到了絕境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田先生 你說話跟舉止就不能再浮誇點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說要拍真實的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再說我就算是做了這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就變成作假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:25.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人就戰勝一組人是真事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個老實記者都讓你演戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我發飆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喝醉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 發 飆 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:50.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你還覺得自己是記者 就別做這些無聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我們這些混黑幫的人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,走在光明正道上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果連自己都看不清前方的路那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就連你的說教都包括在內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你實在是再普通不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這麼幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這麼幹了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎 瀨田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本就不是擺拍 而是捏造了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不配做一名記者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話 這也是沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有家人等著我養
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能失敗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 別打遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前來取材的節目今天要播放了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我事前確認的時候感覺不太有黑幫的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.23,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,452)}特集                                       當代黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.23,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\pos(952,888)\c&H070707&}渴求血與暴力與金錢的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:12:38.94,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\blur2\3c&H28A994&\move(330,330,593.143,375.523,163024,166486)}{\move(354,394,591.143,409.523,163024,166695)}{\fs50\t(163024,166695,\fs30)\c&H030053&\3c&HFFFFFF&}特{\c&H171717&}集 當代黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:12:38.94,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\fs50\blur2\move(354,394,595.143,419.523,163024,166695)}{\fs50\t(163024,166695,\fs30)\3c&HFFFFFF&}渴求{\c&H393CB7&\3c&HFFFFFF&}血{\c&H171717&}與暴力與金錢的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他坐在黑色高級轎車而來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:00.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人闖進敵對勢力的老巢 並將其一舉殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是黑幫電影中極具傳奇色彩的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他究竟是一個怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了錢 錢就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人啊 吃完就扔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在耍我嗎 你這個笨蛋呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,錢 女人 以及暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:26.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人N 到底是經歷過怎樣的人生才會變成現在這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在N小的時候 父親就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從小便過著沒人管的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他還去抓過小混混來打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好當做空手道的練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還能練練危險動作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後被學校停課了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸於打架樂趣中的N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最終沒辦法在家鄉立足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,於是來到東京當起了黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是這樣的他 最初也只不過是想找一個立錐之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:57.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(992,848)}{\bord3\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H171717&\3c&HFFFFFF&}在黑幫老窩的對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他被組織當槍使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他也就逐漸地不再相信別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1470,502)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}為什麼組長對你會是這個態度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1490,174)}{\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1496,890)}{\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那傢伙很傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,0)\pos(1572,534)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}你們之間沒有人情世故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1594,248)}{\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}Q
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1562,834)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是做了這種事 不就變成作假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,當他意識到之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經從昭和俠義黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:16.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,變為了沒有人情世故 稱得上是「平成怪物」的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從他的私人生活中也可以看出他缺少人情味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前和他玩過的女人生了個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他卻說這孩子是他收養的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:29.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們之前還對這個叫N的男人抱有一絲期待 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總是被要求幹這個幹那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘如此回答道 腳還是骨折的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像沒有什麼特別的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,N拒絕承認她是自己女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但她卻說自己是他的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她的樣子真的非常悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對N來說 別人早就已經變成了他的敵人或者生財工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我們採訪了這樣一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種活法 周圍不就全是敵人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 秒殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:06.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後當所有採訪結束 我們準備支付採訪費用時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,N緩緩說道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對著嚇了一跳的我們 N繼續說道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別做這些無聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果連自己都看不清前方的路那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在暗示我們 不再多給點錢的話就弄瞎我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在支付了10倍的金額後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於接受了的N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:30.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊笑著 一邊消失在夜裡的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個充斥著欲望的黑夜中不斷前行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到毀滅為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什麼鬼內容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 平成的怪物先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個笨蛋還真對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟老爹說了後他說要揍扁你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說「小雛不是你女兒到底是怎麼一回事」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那全都是電視台自己動手捏造出來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別做這些無聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:23.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個充斥著欲望的黑夜中不斷前行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到毀滅為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你把節目錄下來背台詞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 那到底算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雛 老是在玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作業做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 秒殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一股黑幫仍未覆滅的感覺
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始請多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:53.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛去了滑雪教室不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:04.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}生剝滑雪教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還想著說正好碰上放假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是要看小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼不跟中華店的大叔他們一起去溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他們說難得去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不想跟著去添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓他們過過二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給多少錢能把你跟雛交換啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:28.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我端出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,端菜我可熟得不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,餐具收拾就讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很擅長洗碗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比想像中要輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡這股煩躁感到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是義史超加強版
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再多教我一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休息 不出去外面玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:15.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想叔叔他們回來的時候能驚喜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:21.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:22.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}義史原創混合清洗劑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 好厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 才會進行比較
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,專業過頭了反而有點噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與雛真是雲泥之別…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 有什麼我能幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用這麼勤奮也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子你是客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 畢竟我受你照顧著嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:04.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會做我力所能及的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,互幫互助是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:22.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:26.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,中華店那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我這邊是雛 他們那邊是杏子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼乖巧懂事的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 怎麼可能有這種孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始也不是現在這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:43.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛相遇的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是個更加依賴力量不講理的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就讓她回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 我們出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說要教我各種小技巧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,兩三天的話綽綽有餘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:01.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的休息日 小孩子都會去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我翻花繩很厲害哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會去玩那麼蠢的遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂的話就跟著來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會教你各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始 雛和杏子並沒有什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是環境讓她們產生了區別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她記住跟雛一樣的娛樂方式的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:35.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子也會回想起任性隨意的孩子本性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,中華店的人也好好體會一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,養育孩子的幸苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要花錢的話不來也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,切 淨是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:48.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 休息日就是獎勵自己的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你叔叔他們也是為了能去旅行而賺錢的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看我不馬上把你的好孩子面具扯下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去溫泉也要花錢的呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:04.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要花錢的話 就能任意玩樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:21.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 慢一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險 突然就被治癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,渾身濕透啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要堅定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是演技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:45.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是當流浪漢時為了生存下去而生出的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂小孩子 是更加忠於自己的欲求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:59.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,光會搗蛋給旁人添麻煩的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 接下來去乘這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快一點快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:10.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了對付這傢伙的治癒攻擊而製造出來的機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來很享受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:19.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 乘了這個後接下來就去新田想去的項目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 去杏子你喜歡的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,平時不能提的任性要求今天都可以說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果休息日是愉快玩耍的日子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是兩個人都樂在其中就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:41.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我比較想要跟新田一起開心享受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比較好……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:03.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒所謂了吧 就做個夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就做個夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:25.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做夢吧 做夢吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:45.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:48.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,當爸的想要的理想型女兒 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是叔叔他們回來的日子 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:20.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:22.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:30.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:33.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸在理想型中 都要忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要回來了嗎 現實！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喊我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是新田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是渡邊中學的松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上現在舉辦中的滑雪教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:54.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然實在是難以辯解…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田雛在雪山裡遇難了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:05.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
